replies.body:
I like {{item:3056}} on {{champion:12}}, the item was practically made for him and he can easily rush it.

However most other champs can't, because it's a purely defensive item and they need to get some damage first.
So it would be nice to replace {{item:3067}} with something a little more offensive like {{item:3044}} or {{item:3108}}{{item:1028}}
